<div><div id='zzq9pludosamgh3RiverDetailGadget2' class='CRiverDetailGadget-detail CRiverDetailGadget'><div class='controls'><h1>Naugatuck - 2) South Waterbury&ndash;Beacon Falls</h1>
<div><div id='zzq9pludosamgh3ArticleGadget26Container' class='CArticleGadget-view CArticleGadget'><div id='zzq9pludosamgh3ArticleGadget26-1' class='contents'></div></div> <br style='clear:both'>
