<div class='commentinfo comment_comment'>
2011-08-23 08:24:21 (1012 days ago)
<div id='contact-153212'>mrod911 (153212)</div> </div>
<div class='commentbox'>
This is a nice class ii stretch, at the right levels. At a guage of level of 3, although navigable,<br/>
some sections are just too low. The most interesting sections are a couple of boulder gardens with<br/>
a large number of eddies offering good opportunities for skill building or skill refining. Access<br/>
to these sections is tricky and are better combined with the whole run. </div>
</td>
</tr>
